<p>
	Great! Now on to turning this into a website. No problem. First things first, fire up your favorite text
	editor. (Notepad works fine to start with if you're on	Windows. For Mac, TextEdit works if you set it to
	use Plain Text mode in the preferences. And color me surprised if you're on Linux and don't already have
	a favorite text editor!) Now let's type out all the words from our design:
</p>

<pre class="prettyprint lang-html">My Super Blog
I write about super things.

Home
About Me
Contact Me

Super Bowling Analysis

Pros: Bowling is super and super is awesome, so super bowling is super awesome.

Cons: There are no cons.

Verdict: I'm for it.

